{
  "total_duration": 759.137,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.552,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Through the forest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“穿过森林”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 5.902,
      "end": 16.062,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先说清楚一个 safety boundary：课文里的 Mrs. Sterling 很勇敢，但现实里如果有人抢包、抢手机、抢钱包，孩子绝对不要追。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 16.412,
      "end": 29.252,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "真实生活里，第一件事是 protect yourself and other people，保护自己和身边的人；然后 shout for help，往人多的地方走，找大人、保安，或者 call the police。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 29.601,
      "end": 37.761,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天我们学的不是“怎样追坏人”，而是怎样用英语把一串动作讲得像电影镜头一样清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 38.111,
      "end": 50.399,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事从一个 calm picnic 开始。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Picnic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 outdoor meal，户外野餐；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at the edge of a forest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是在森林边上，不是在森林深处。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 50.749,
      "end": 61.989,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以想象：open grass，野餐垫，孩子，旁边就是 trees。突然，two men rush up，想抢 Mrs. Sterling 的 handbag。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 62.339,
      "end": 76.259,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后动作链一格一格推进：rushed up -> tried to steal -> strap broke -> ran through the trees -> ran after them -> out of breath -> caught up -> went through the contents -> dropped the bag。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 76.609,
      "end": 84.209,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结尾反而很 calm：包带坏了，需要修；但 nothing was stolen，什么也没被偷走。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 84.558,
      "end": 105.278,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天记忆链是：picnic -> edge of forest -> rushed up -> tried to steal -> strap broke -> bag in their possession -> ran through trees -> ran after them -> out of breath -> caught up -> contents of the bag -> ran straight at them -> fright -> dropped the bag -> strap needs mending。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 105.628,
      "end": 115.82,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 forest edge picnic。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Anne Sterling did not think of the risk she was taking when she ran through a forest after two men."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 116.17,
      "end": 122.082,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Risk"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 danger，风险。她后来追进森林，其实很危险。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 122.432,
      "end": 131.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着课文倒回去解释事情怎么开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They had rushed up to her while she was having a picnic at the edge of a forest with her children."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 132.318,
      "end": 143.606,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at the edge of a forest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是 deep in the forest。她和孩子们是在森林边上的开放区域野餐，旁边有树，所以后面两个人可以跑进树林。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 143.955,
      "end": 152.075,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一帧要先安静：blanket，food，children，trees。越 calm，后面的 sudden action 越明显。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 152.425,
      "end": 161.585,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是 sudden grab and broken strap。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They had rushed up to her and tried to steal her handbag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 161.935,
      "end": 170.247,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Rush up to her"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是突然快速冲到她跟前；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "steal"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是拿走不属于自己的东西。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 170.597,
      "end": 178.085,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文没有直接说 a long fight，只给了关键动作："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In the struggle, the strap broke."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 178.435,
      "end": 187.242,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Struggle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是争抢、拉扯；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "strap"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是包带；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "broke"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是断了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 187.592,
      "end": 196.644,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后 bag 的位置变了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "with the bag in their possession"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，包落到他们手里。这个物品位置变化，就是 chase 的开关。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 196.994,
      "end": 206.37,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是 through the trees。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "With the bag in their possession, both men started running through the trees."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 206.72,
      "end": 212.495,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "through"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是穿过、在树林之间跑过去。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 212.845,
      "end": 219.621,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Mrs. Sterling 的情绪推动下一步："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Sterling got so angry that she ran after them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 219.971,
      "end": 227.155,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "So angry that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“气到某种程度，所以做了后面的动作”。她气得追了上去。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 227.505,
      "end": 233.785,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但课文也马上让你看到风险："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She was soon out of breath, but she continued to run."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 234.135,
      "end": 243.87,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Out of breath"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是上气不接下气。她已经喘了，可是还继续跑。电影感来自动作一个接一个，不是来自夸张打斗。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 244.22,
      "end": 253.932,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是 such a fright。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she caught up with them, she saw that they had sat down and were going through the contents of the bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 254.282,
      "end": 260.834,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Catch up with"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是追上；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "contents"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是里面的东西。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 261.184,
      "end": 272.176,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里有一个重要短语："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "go through the contents"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它不是“穿过内容”，而是 search，look through，翻看包里的东西。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 272.526,
      "end": 276.805,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后最后一串动作来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She ran straight at them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 277.155,
      "end": 281.499,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The men got such a fright that they dropped the bag and ran away."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 281.849,
      "end": 290.537,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Such a fright that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“吓了这么一大跳，所以产生了后面的结果”。他们把包扔下，跑了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 290.887,
      "end": 301.335,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一行很有 New Concept 的 dry humor："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The strap needs mending, but they did not steal anything."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "包带要修，但东西没丢。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 301.685,
      "end": 304.525,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易学错的地方是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 304.875,
      "end": 309.49,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "会不会觉得 Mrs. Sterling 很勇敢，所以现实里也应该追？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 309.84,
      "end": 319.44,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这个一定不能学错。故事里她很 brave，但 real life safety 不一样。现实里不要 chase thieves，不要 fight for a bag。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 319.79,
      "end": 321.956,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那应该怎么办？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 322.306,
      "end": 334.266,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Keep yourself safe，保护孩子或者身边的人，shout for help，move toward other people，找大人、保安或者报警，还可以记住他们往哪个方向跑、穿什么衣服。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 334.616,
      "end": 336.518,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那我们主要学什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 336.868,
      "end": 346.228,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "学 action chain writing，动作链写作法。课文不是总结一句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She got her handbag back."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，而是让你看见每一步。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 346.577,
      "end": 351.289,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如 rushed up，strap broke，ran through the trees，ran after them？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 351.639,
      "end": 360.319,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Yes. 再加上 out of breath，caught up，going through the contents，ran straight at them，dropped the bag and ran away。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 360.669,
      "end": 362.563,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以像短电影一样？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 362.913,
      "end": 371.513,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Exactly. A calm picnic turns into a fast action scene, and then ends with one very practical sentence about the broken strap."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 371.863,
      "end": 377.791,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Anne Sterling did not think of the risk she was taking when she ran through a forest after two men."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 378.141,
      "end": 384.813,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They had rushed up to her while she was having a picnic at the edge of a forest with her children and tried to steal her handbag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 385.163,
      "end": 391.715,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In the struggle, the strap broke and, with the bag in their possession, both men started running through the trees."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 392.065,
      "end": 395.881,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Sterling got so angry that she ran after them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 396.23,
      "end": 400.094,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She was soon out of breath, but she continued to run."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 400.444,
      "end": 407.356,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she caught up with them, she saw that they had sat down and were going through the contents of the bag, so she ran straight at them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 407.706,
      "end": 411.69,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The men got such a fright that they dropped the bag and ran away."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
